comments[5]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-12T15:41:03.738Z",maintainer-agent,"Live reliability evidence 2026-07-12: PM-CLI-10 remains the second 14-day Sentry gate blocker; latest event is handled=true ERR_MODULE_NOT_FOUND from the operator host on release 2026.7.12 and matches this item's torn-install signature. Current build/packed-consumer and 10k/100k performance dogfood do not reproduce it. Resolving the already-triaged event group pending this item's distinct bundle-integrity code fix; genuine module failures remain blocking by design."
  "2026-07-12T18:10:50.205Z",maintainer-agent,"Live recurrence 2026-07-12 17:27Z: PM-CLI-26 count is now 2. Latest handled production event on release pm-cli@2026.7.12 reports stale chunk-BVCWZQR4.js missing createStdinTokenResolver; the earlier event used a different stale chunk/export. This strengthens the canonical torn-generation diagnosis and acceptance criteria; no duplicate item created. Current build, full 5588-test coverage, installed-package dogfood, and strict 10k benchmark do not reproduce it. Resolving the observed group pending the distinct bundle-integrity code implementation; genuine module failures remain gate-blocking."
  "2026-07-13T19:42:44.077Z",codex-root,"Live recurrence evidence 2026-07-13 from the release gate: PM-CLI-26 is unresolved high with count=3, first seen 2026-07-11 and last seen 2026-07-13T18:50Z; newest signature is a stale bundle chunk missing runUpdate. The context packer/feedback suite, packed install, 10k scale gate, and package-first dogfood do not reproduce it. This remains the canonical torn-install class; no duplicate item created or claimed."
  "2026-07-14T00:09:48.356Z",codex-gpt5,"Implementation evidence: build now atomically emits a SHA-256 bundle generation manifest; startup converts only manifest-proven partial-upgrade/concurrent-build module failures to bundle_integrity_torn_install, while intact-manifest module failures remain blocking. Reliability gate allowlist is exact-code only. Focused bundle/startup/gate regressions plus all strict gates and 100/100/100/100 coverage pass."
  "2026-07-14T00:29:12.227Z",codex-root,"Final verification: pm linked bundle/gate suite passes 74/74; packed tarball contains a valid 188-file SHA-256 manifest; npx smoke and 88-command dogfood pass; live Sentry/telemetry gate reports critical=0 high=0, error rate=0.27%, and zero missing error-code rows. PM-CLI-26 is resolved."
